txt.en: 'Outside Seregost guarded by Blight Lady's children. Know about them? Merrevail, they called. Most dangerous thing in swamp. Maybe. Smarter than Orcs and can fly! Better be careful.'
Stained merrevail can be found near Seregost.\n\nYou should defeat any Stained merrevail you find.

The merrevail guarding the front of Seregost have been vanquished. If these are truly the children of Lhaereth the Stained, you wonder what manner of creature she is and if she has more ghastly children awaiting you inside.
'Outside Seregost guarded by Blight Lady's children. Know about them? Merrevail, they called. Most dangerous thing in swamp. Maybe. Smarter than Orcs and can fly! Better be careful.'
Viznak has mentioned that the area near Seregost is heavily patrolled by Lhaereth's children: the Merrevail. You should defeat any you encounter.
